    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
