      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s ready for a brand new adventure! \ud83d\ude97 It\u2019s been such a fantastic, reliable ride for me\u2014runs smooth as butter and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's got that perfect balance of being broken-in just right while still looking and feeling great on the road. Whether you're zipping to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin and see why I\u2019ve enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
