      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio for a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal front-engine, rear-drive layout utilizes a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock to maximize mechanical grip. The chassis features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a weight-saving carbon fiber roof to optimize the center of gravity. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems perform to factory tolerances. A mechanically sound example of BMW's final naturally aspirated M-car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
